Paper: hep-th/0009130

Date: 2000-09-16

Title: Self-Duality of a Topologically Massive Born-Infeld Theory

Authors: Prasanta K. Tripathy and Avinash Khare

Comments: 10 Pages, Accepted in Phys. Lett. B, New results and references added

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B504 (2001) 152-156

We consider self-duality in a 2+1 dimensional gauge theory containing boththe Born-Infeld and the Chern-Simons terms. We introduce a Born-Infeld inspiredgeneralization of the Proca term and show that the corresponding self dualequation is identical to that of the Born-Infeld-Chern-Simons theory.